Package: GVEMGRM
Type: Package
Title: Gaussian Variational Expectation Maximization for
        Multidimensional Graded Response Model
Version: 0.0
Date: 2025-05-03
Author: 
  Qian Zhen Zheng [aut],
  Laixu Shang [aut, cre],
  Ping Feng Xu [aut],
  Na Shan [aut],
  Zhigen Gao [aut]
Maintainer: Laixu Shang <laixu3107@foxmail.com>
Description: 
    This R package implements a Gaussian Variational Expectation Maximization (GVEM) 
    algorithm for estimating item parameters in the multidimensional graded response
    model. It supports both confirmatory and exploratory analyses of Likert-scale
    response data with high-dimensional latent traits. Additionally,
    an importance-weighted GVEM (IW-GVEM) algorithm is included to reduce bias
    in the estimation of the loading matrix during confirmatory analysis.
